msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah... <2.pa>It must have felt quite cold to you,\n"
"didn't it?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I had a great plan, you know. I left\n"
"Rito Village to try to earn some money\n"
"out in the world...\n"
"<2.so>But it's so incredibly hot here during the\n"
"day.<3.pa> It's been tough to work up the will\n"
"to go any farther.\n"
"I would like to see what Gerudo Town\n"
"looks like, even if I can't go inside...<4.pa>\n"
"It's just so hot..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>But before I say any more...<2.pa>\n"
"Have we...<3.pa>met before?"
msgstr ""

