msgctxt "talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.se_co><2.so><3.re_co>I heard there's an <4.se_co>elixir that can help"
" \n"
"beat the heat<5.re_co>. It's made from <6.se_co>insects \n"
"with cooling effects <7.re_co>and <8.se_co>monster parts<9.re_co>.\n"
"<10.so>But they don't seem to be selling the\n"
"elixir anywhere...<11.pa>\n"
"\n"
"I've heard <12.se_co>insects with these cooling \n"
"effects<13.re_co> live in <14.se_co>the cold parts of the\n"
"Gerudo Highlands<15.re_co>, but...\n"
"<16.so>Well, the monsters there are rough, to\n"
"say the least,<17.pa> so I'm not having a lot of\n"
"success getting myself motivated..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hm?<2.pa>\n"
"Oof...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"Looks like I fell asleep..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I never knew the desert in the middle of\n"
"the day could get so darned hot.\n"
"\n"
"I guess you can't really understand\n"
"something until you've experienced it\n"
"for yourself, huh...<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Far to the north of here...<2.pa>\n"
"It's a modest village on the\n"
"<3.se_co>Tabantha Frontier<4.re_co>..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk15"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm going to have to get my young one\n"
"to get out and travel too...someday..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk19"
msgid ""
"<1.so>With the elixir, I can go as soon as I\n"
"want, but... <2.pa>Well, the desert isn't all that\n"
"safe at night.\n"
"I think I'll wait till it's light out."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk20"
msgid ""
"<1.so>With the elixir, I can go as soon as I\n"
"want, but...<2.pa>there's no rush, really.\n"
"I think I'll leave tomorrow."
msgstr ""

